'''Terra Sool militia fighters''' were operated by the [[Terra Sool militia|militia]] of [[Terra Sool]]. They fought under the banner of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

The fighters were single-seater ships shaped like a rounded flying wing, similar in shape to the [[DC0052 speeder]].
They fared poorly against [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|CIS]] [[Conqueror-class atmospheric dreadnaught|Floating Battle Platforms]] during the battle.

